code: @Override protected NodeInfo<GreaterThan> info() {     return NodeInfo.create(this, GreaterThan::new, left(), right()). }
@Override protected GreaterThan replaceChildren(Expression newLeft, Expression newRight) {     return new GreaterThan(source(), newLeft, newRight). }
@Override public LessThan swapLeftAndRight() {     return new LessThan(source(), right(), left()). }
@Override public LessThanOrEqual negate() {     return new LessThanOrEqual(source(), left(), right()). }
